===Pronunciation===
[[Category:Hebrew language]]
אור / 'ôr / ore

===Etymology===
From אור  {{HH|215}}; 

===Noun===
'''אור'''

# illumination or (concretely) luminary (in every sense, including lightning, happiness, etc.): - bright, clear, + [[day]], [[light]] (-ning), morning, sun.

